.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-PEER-SUMMARY" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-peer-summary \- show channels aggregated by peer
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-peer-summary
.SH DESCRIPTION
Lists all peer channels grouped and aggregated by peer_id, showing channel count and balance totals per peer.
.PP
Output: JSON array of peer summary objects with peer_id, channels, total_msat, local_msat.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-peer-list-connected (1),
.BR lightning-channel-balance-ratio (1)
